        {
            "+content": "Seventeen-year-old Rei Sugiyama wins a ticket to an anime convention in Tokyo with <i>Yukikaze</i> and <i>Stratos 4</i> as its headliners. Upon arriving at the convention, he enters the men's room, only to find himself transported into the planet Fairy, where he encounters the fighting fairies Mave, Super Sylph, and Sylphied. There, Rei also learns that the surrounding and the characters are figments of imagination from anime fans, but now the fairies must protect him from the JAM and the monster known as the Forgetter while fearing for their existence due to the changing interests of fans.",
